body: https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/35953 has moved `VersionedSelector` related dictionaries under `PhysicsTools/SelectorUtils` as this is the package which defines `VersionedSelector<T>`. This change fixes the dictionary/package mapping for `VersionedSelector`
title: added VersionedSelector dict mapping to PhysicsTools/SelectorUtils
